          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你侧着宜春髻子，恰凭栏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "剪不断，理还乱，闷无端！"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已吩咐催花莺燕借春看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春香，可曾吩咐花郎扫除花径么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "已扫除清净了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取镜台、衣服过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云髻罢梳还对镜，罗衣欲换更添香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，镜台、衣服在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好天气也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（步步娇） 枭晴丝吹闲庭院，"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请小姐梳妆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐请行一步。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（醉扶归） 你道翠生生出落的裙衫儿茜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春香！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（醉扶归） 可知我常一生儿爱好是天然。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春香——"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是花园门首，请小姐进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "进得园来，你看："
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "画廊金粉半零星，"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是金鱼池。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "池馆苍苔一片青。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "踏草怕泥新绣袜，惜花疼煞小金铃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不到园林，怎知春色如许。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "便是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "春香——"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，这是青山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是杜鹃花。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是荼蘼架。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是花多开，牡丹还早。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，你看莺燕叫得好听啊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，这园子委实观之不足。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提它怎么！"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "留些余兴，明日再来耍子罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（隔尾） 观之不足由他缱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，你身子乏了，歇息片时。我去看看老夫人再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去去就来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瓶插映山紫，炉添沉水香。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（春香下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "默地游春转，小试宜春面。春啊春，得和你两留连，春去如何遣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉，恁般天气，好困人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山坡羊） 没乱里春情难遣，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（万年欢牌。杜丽娘入梦，柳梦梅上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐！小生哪一处不寻到，却在这里！恰好在花园内，折得垂柳半枝；姐姐你"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那生素昧平生，因何到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐咱一片幽情，爱煞你哩！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山桃红） 则为你如花美眷，似水流年，"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐我和你那答儿讲话去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喏！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山桃红） 转过这芍药栏前，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（柳梦梅、杜丽娘同下。众花神引大花神同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "催花御史惜花天，"
        },
        {
          "character": "众花神",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "检点春光又一年。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蘸客伤心红雨下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "众花神",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "勾人悬梦彩云边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃南安府后花园花神是也。今有杜小姐游春伤感，致辞使柳秀才入梦。吾神"
        },
        {
          "character": "众花神",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾等万紫千红，正宜他惜玉怜香。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同画眉序） 好景艳阳天，万紫千红尽开遍。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同滴溜子） 湖山畔，湖山畔云缠雨绵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（同鲍老催） 单则是混阳蒸变，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待咱拈片落花惊醒他。呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲍老催） 他梦酣春透了怎留连，"
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "柳秀才，你梦毕之时，好生送杜小姐仍归香阁。吾神去也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（万年欢牌。众花神、大花神同下。柳梦梅、杜丽娘携手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐你身子乏了，将息片时。小生去也。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "大花神",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行来春色三分雨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秀才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "柳梦梅",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "睡去巫山一片云。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（柳梦梅下。杜母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫婿坐黄堂，娇娃立绣窗。怪她裙衩上，花鸟绣双双。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，秀……"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，为娘在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是母亲。母亲万福。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，你方才说什么秀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦……孩儿说剌绣才罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何昼眠在此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告母亲知道：孩儿适才往后花园游玩回来，不觉身子困倦，少睡片时。不知母"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么不到学堂中看书？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生不在，且自消停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，花园冷静，少去闲游。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谨依慈命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妇儿家长成了，自有这许多情态。且自由她，我去了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宛转随女儿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿送母亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辛勤做老娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杜母下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜丽娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘啊，你教孩儿看书，不知哪一种书，才消得我的闷怀哟！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（绵搭絮） 雨香云片，才到梦儿边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（春香上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晚妆销粉印，春润费香篝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "春香",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，薰了被窝睡吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
